# STATS::STAT_GET_VEHICLE_BAIL_DISTANCE

## Summary
Get the last bail out of vehicle distance

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Travel the furthest distance when bailing from a vehicle
